                                <div class="institutional-banners__title">
                                    Invest in Bitcoin via BTCE
                                </div>
                                <div class="institutional-banners__text">
                                    The world’s first centrally cleared exchange traded product (ETP) on Bitcoin
                                </div>
                                <div class="institutional-banners__desc">
                                    ITI Capital provides block trading access to institutional investors via BTCE
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <a href="#" class="institutional-banners__link">Get started today -></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="institutional-banners__item">
                        <div class="institutional-banners__item-wrap">
                            <div class="institutional-banners__bg institutional-banners__bg--zeth"></div>
                            <div class="institutional-banners__data">
                                <div class="institutional-banners__title">
                                    Invest in Ethereum via ZETH
